operator EISCAT staff
submitter Kjellmar Oksavik
resources NO(3)
notes
The purpose of this experiment is to look for mesoscale flow channels to the 
magnetic northeast. The experiment is a 192 second windscreen wiper scan at 30 
deg elevation with the 32m antenna. Azimuth varies between -30 to 90, and data 
is taken with the 32m antenna only. Start the experiment in the following way:

poweron
cd /external/kst/tau0/510
runexperiment tau0.elan fullminute KOscanAZne NO 3.2

PLEASE NOTE: This particular experiment shall ONLY be run from 06:00-09:00 UT. 
There is a slightly different experiment for 09:00–12:00 UT (see schedule, the 
scan pattern differs).
